---
title: Sweet Corn Butter Masala with golden cheese and coriander
description: With butter, golden fried cheese and juicy sweet corn, this is a dish that's undeniably rich. The mix of North Indian spices and fresh coriander balances things out with just enough brightness and bite to create a well-rounded recipe you're sure to love.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF230130_R09_W11_IE_IEQVV13085-2_Main_high-c94d70f7.jpg
